title: Skills section with always-loaded vs available distinction
---
Inject a Skills section into the prompt that distinguishes: (a) skills currently loaded into context, and (b) skills available but not yet loaded (by name + brief description). Mirrors nullclaw's skills section. Enables the agent to reference or request skill loading without hallucinating capabilities.